#div1 {

height: 150px;

width: 400px;

margin: 20px;

border: 1px solid red;

padding: 10px;

}

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Height = margin-top + border-top + padding-top + (height of the content)+ padding-bottom + border-bottom + margin-bottom

Width = margin-left + border-left + padding-left + (width of the content)+ padding-right + border-right + margin-right

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Height = 20 + 1 + 10 + 150 + 10 + 1 + 20 = 212

Width = 20 + 1 + 10 + 400 + 10 + 1 + 20 = 462

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Browser calculated width: border-left + padding-left + (width of the content)+ padding-right + border-right

Browser calculated height: border-top + padding-top + (height of the content)+ padding-bottom + border-bottom 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

